title: Meet Kaley Cuocos Newly Adopted Puppy Chester
text:
Meet Kaley Cuoco's Newly Adopted Puppy, Chester 
E online Saturday 24th October, 2015 
can't say no to a cute furry face.The actress and animal lover revealed that she decided to expand her four-legged brood by sharing a few snapshots on her Instagram of her newly adopted pooch, Chester...
